  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient scheduled for coronary artery bypass graft surgery and/or aortic valve
             replacement with extra-corporeal circulation

          -  Patient in sinus rhythm at the time of surgery

          -  Patient older than 18

          -  Patient able to understand the information and consent forms

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Medical history of type 2 diabetes, atrial fibrillation or use of class III
             anti-arhythmic drug

          -  left ventricle ejection fraction &lt; 40%

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Patient in emergency condition
      </textblock>
